#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QComboBox, keyboardModelComboBox)
#: kcm_keyboard.ui:53
#, fuzzy, kde-format
msgid ""
"Here you can choose a keyboard model. This setting is independent of your "
"keyboard layout and refers to the \"hardware\" model, i.e. the way your "
"keyboard is manufactured. Modern keyboards that come with your computer "
"usually have two extra keys and are referred to as \"104-key\" models, which "
"is probably what you want if you do not know what kind of keyboard you "
"have.\n"
msgstr ""
"Apha ungakhetha uhlobo lwebhodi yezitshixo. Olu cwangciso luxhomekeke kubeko "
"lwebhodi yezitshixo yakho kwaye ibhekisa  kwindlela ye \"hardware\", ithetha "
"ukuba indlela ibhodi yakho yezitshixo eyenziwe ngayo. Iibhodi zezitshixo "
"zexesha langoku eziza nekhompyutha yakho ziqhele ukuba nezitshixo "
"ezongezelelweyo ezimbini kwaye zibhekiswa njenge \"104-key\"iintlobo, apho "
"iyeyona nto uyifunayo ukuba awulazi udidi lwebhodi yezitshixo onayo."

